    "Multilingual forms: Russian ``Когда `X` тогда `Y` `` / ``Когда `X` делай `Y` ``, Hindi ``जब `X` तब `Y` ``, Chinese ``当 `X` 时 `Y` ``.",
    "The write is append-only: export memory to preserve the rule message with the dialog.",
